## Additional Terms for Educational Use

This software is specifically designed for educational institutions and learning purposes. 
The author encourages its use in educational settings and welcomes contributions from 
the educational community.

### Attribution Notice

When using this software in educational institutions, please consider providing 
attribution by including:

"Powered by School Management System by Ishara Lakshitha Bandara"

This attribution helps support the continued development of educational technology
solutions and encourages collaboration within the educational community.

### Educational Support

For educational institutions requiring assistance with implementation or customization,
please reach out to the project maintainers. We are committed to supporting educational
initiatives and helping institutions make the most of this system.

Contact: https://github.com/isharax9/School-management-system
